<p>
  What is the matrix for <m>R_\theta</m>?
</p>

<assemblage xml:id="matrix-for-rotation">
<p>
<term>Fact:</term> The matrix corresponding to the rotation transformation <m>R_\theta</m> is 
<md>
  A_{R_\theta} = \begin{bmatrix} \cos\theta \amp -\sin\theta \\ \sin\theta \amp \cos\theta\end{bmatrix}.
</md>
</p>
</assemblage>

<p> 
  We illustrate this with an acute angle in <xref ref="fig-matrix-rotation"/>.
</p>

